 ~/ t.trandist
 ~/ emme2 clear 321 batch -m "t.trandist"
 ~/ DML 3.2.92
 ~/ ms10,ms12,ms14  - x coordinate of metros
 ~/ ms11,ms13,ms15  - y coordinate of metros
 ~/ mo27 x coordinate of centroid
 ~/ mo28 y coordinate of centroid
